data.description: Luxury and comfort converge at in the Legacy Grove Community, Athens, AL. This 4-bed, 3-bath home features hardwood floors, new bedroom carpets, and tiled wet areas. Fresh paint sets the stage for your personal touch. Intricate trim work accentuates the living spaces. A double-sided fireplace links the great room to the vaulted sunroom. The kitchen, adorned with granite, includes a pantry. The master suite is a private haven with a double trey ceiling, sitting area, and a spa-like bath. Two bedrooms share a full bath, and the 4th bedroom has an attached full bath. A 3-car garage completes this offering. Qualified buyers may receive up to $4,000 credit for closing costs. Call for details.
